data.description: An incredibly scarce chance awaits you to possess a small fragment of Trujillo Creek. This beautiful property spans 49 acres and features wooded areas, picturesque meadows, and hay fields. Rich in wildlife, this land is a haven for elk, deer, bobcats, turkeys, and more.  The home on this property offers an open floor plan that creates a welcoming atmosphere. Cozy up to the wood-burning stove on chilly nights in the great room.  The kitchen complete with an island, is perfect for preparing meals, and the dining room offers an elegant space with a built-in China hutch and separate wet bar.  With three bedrooms and two full baths, this home is spacious enough to accommodate your family and guests.  Whether you're an outdoor enthusiast or a hunter, there's ample room for all your gear with a large storage building and two additional storage sheds on the property. This property includes water and mineral rights, adding immense value to this already incredible land!  This mountainous property offers a great opportunity to embrace the Colorado wilderness and create your own slice of paradise. Don't miss your chance to own this extraordinary piece of real estate where the beauty of nature surrounds you! Contact us today to schedule a viewing and start your journey to mountain living.
